        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: 'After their \"declaration\" to the world, the whole world was left in shock.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Yes, after all, it was the first time that a human group declared a \"break\" from humanity.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: 'After that, even the newly integrated World Government Intelligence Agency was mobilized for this purpose.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 31,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'You know how it ended. They had planned for it.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 32,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: '...It\\'s amazing that they managed to put everyone in hiding before making that kind of \"declaration.\"', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 33,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: 'It\\'s not inconceivable. Everyone knew that the School of Sapiens was preparing for something, just not that they were planning to \"break\" from humanity.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 34,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: '—At that time, humanity was booming and the Golden Age was about to usher in a paradigm shift with interstellar colonization.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'If you had announced at that time that you were going to break from humanity, I would\\'ve thought you were crazy.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: '...Yet they still did it.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 37,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Correct. And only now did we rediscover their existence.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 38,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: '...Who knows if the Gray Ravens have been able to carry out their mission without any issues.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 39,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Asimov just informed me over the comms that they\\'ve gone significantly deeper underground, which has temporarily disabled remote communication.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 40,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: '...Are you worried about them?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'There\\'s no point in being worried.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'I think we can believe 【kuroname】.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 43,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: 'Because the commandant is a Chief from F.O.S.?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 44,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'No, because of 【kuroname】\\'s belief in others.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 45,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Even if 【kuroname】 sees the darkness buried within this world, the commandant still manages to find one\\'s own direction in life.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 46,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: '...I really have no idea how you have so much insight into others.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 47,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'That\\'s why I am the President, and you are not.', 4: '2'}"
    },
